   version   stable 0.8.15 0.8.10 0.8.8
   version unstable 0.9.1
   require GConf gtk+ libgsf
  category development
 attribute gnome library makej multilib-concurrent
    source $GNOME_URL sources/goffice/${VERSION:0:3}/goffice-$VERSION.tar.bz2
      info last  20110522
      info home  http://www.gnumeric.org/
      info docs  http://projects.gnome.org/gnumeric/doc/gnumeric.shtml
      info mail  http://mail.gnome.org/mailman/listinfo/gnumeric-list
